    public abstract class BaseMultiStateLfAlgorithmImpl<TNet extends AclfNetwork>
extends NetworkRefImpl<TNet>
implements BaseMultiStateLfAlgorithm<TNet>
    An implementation of the model object 'FS Loadflow Algorithm'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • One Net2 Multi Lf Algo
    • Fixed Structure
    • NOf Lf Algoritms
    • Ms Aclf Net List
